TV Independent weighed in on the never-ending rivalry discussion by asking Nigerians of who they think is the best between Cristiano Ronaldo (the diliget Portuguese skipper and current forward player for Juventus FC of Italy) and Lionel Messi (the Argentine Skipper and the indefatigable legend of FC Barcelona of Spain). Who do you think is the best – C.Ronaldo or Leo Messi? Leave your thoughts in the comment section below. —
